# Difference when we use Set and priority_queue for Dijkstra's Algorithm

1. Advantages of Set
  A priority_queue does not give ease to search and directly deletion.
  so, we just need to add better distance pair without excluding it but in set
  before adding a new shorter distance pair we can delete the older when because of this 
  then memory requirement becomes lower and we escapes the few iteration.

2. Advantages of priority_queue
  A set is Red_Black Tree which takes higher time to search elements rather than queue which 
  uses vector and works faster.
